author: DAVID J. CRIBLEZ
title: Joe Walsh adds tickets to his Westbury show
text:
Life's been good to Joe Walsh so far and now he wants to share it with his fans.
The Eagles guitarist is set to play a sold-out solo show at the NYCB Theatre at Westbury on Wednesday, Oct. 14, and he decided to release some extra tickets for his fans.
"Hey Long Island! We just opened up some more seats so I can play this really cool theater in the round!" Walsh said in a statement. "A few great seats now available -- get 'em while they last!"
Tickets ($39.50) can be purchased by visiting ticketmaster.com, calling 800-745-3000 or going to the NYCB Theatre at Westbury box office Tuesday, Oct. 13.
